  "Description": {
    "English": "A piece of otherworldy technology. Its inviting membranes are soft, gel-like, pulsing with a gentle crimson radiance.<br><br>Its warm embrace allows the user to extricate any <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Vile Spawn</span> from the embryotic sacs of <span class=\"name name-special\">Hungering Tendrils</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一件不可思议的高科技物品。这种装置的接入膜有着凝胶般的柔软质地，而且还在不停闪烁着柔和的猩红色光芒。<br><br>其温暖的腔室能够允许使用者从<span class=\"name name-special\">饥饿的触手</span>留下的发育囊中提取<span class=\"name name-stellar\">邪恶滋生</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一項來自異界的科技。柔軟、具膠質感的誘人薄膜，脈動著柔和的緋紅微光。<br><br>其溫暖的環抱，讓使用者從<span class=\"name name-special\">飢渴觸手</span>的胚囊上取下<span class=\"name name-stellar\">汙穢之卵</span>。"
  },
